Note:
Mobile Form Components Module for Mobile UI Framework

This module provides comprehensive form components optimized for mobile input.
Includes various input types, validation, keyboard management, and mobile-specific
form patterns with touch-friendly interactions and platform-native styling.

Key Features:
- Text input fields with validation
- Specialized input types (email, phone, numeric)
- Date and time pickers
- Dropdown selectors and pickers
- Multi-line text areas
- Switch and checkbox inputs
- Slider and stepper controls
- Form validation and error handling
- Keyboard avoidance and management
- Auto-fill and suggestions
- Form state management
- Accessibility compliance

Provides complete form component system for building intuitive mobile
form interfaces with proper validation and user experience.
:End Note

